\begin_layout Subsection*
Appendix B
\end_layout

\begin_layout Labeling
\labelwidthstring 00.00.0000
Question
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

1: 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

The game is over.
 Do you think it was your fault it is over, your colleagues fault, or do
 you think it was because of some other reason?
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 with the possible answers being 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Yes
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

No
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Other reason
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Labeling
\labelwidthstring 00.00.0000
Question
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

2: 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

What strategy did you use while playing this game?
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

, where participants could answer in free text.
\end_layout

